@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_oyqwcb(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.exp(((v1 + 0.99 + v2 + 0.11) + (v2 + 0.44 + v1 + 0.22)))
    v0 = (v2 - (wp.cos(tmp + 0.35) / 0.94))
    v1 = tmp
    v1 = 0.70
    data[tid] = v0
